quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  101,1,"The sudden, mighty strike"
  101,2,"What is the sudden, mighty strike"
  101,3,"What enables you to perceive what the sudden, mighty strike is"
  101,4,The day (when it occurs) humans will be like moths scattered about
  101,5,And the mountains will be like carded wool
  101,6,"And then, the one whose scales are heavy (with faith and good deeds)"
  101,7,He will be in a life of contentment
  101,8,Whereas the one whose scales are light (as devoid of faith and accepted good deeds)
  101,9,He will have his home in a bottomless pit
  101,10,What enables you to perceive what it is
  101,11,It is a fire burning fiercely